headline: GoodHive is an innovative recruitment platform designed to empower the rapidly growing Web3 ecosystem. We are a community of dedicated entrepreneurs with a mission to tackle one of Web3's biggest challenges – the shortage of IT talent. To address this, we’ve launched Web3TalentFair.tech, a job fair connecting top-tier talent in Web3 and the Future of Work industries. As we expand, we’re excited to unveil the Minimum Viable Product (MVP) of our platform. Additionally, through our partnership with IT Unchained, we enable French-based clients to benefit from a 30% tax credit on freelancer costs through our "Agrément Innovation" status.
